description: Enjoy the luxury of owning this two-bedroom, one-and-a-half-bath condo with garage parking. Ideally located within steps of the Broadway shops and minutes to the Seaport, this well-maintained unit, constructed in 2003, features an open living/kitchen/dining room floor plan leading to an oversized composite deck with breathtaking, unobstructed views of the Seaport and the Financial District, and Downtown. The two bedrooms, one en suite, are generously spacious, easily accommodating king-size beds. Other features include HVAC, in-unit laundry, hardwood floors, and extra storage in the deep garage.
